videos.description: Florida's Mike White says his team's gritty defense and attention to detail led to the 75-49 upset of No. 6 Tennessee.
videos.headline: White credits Gators' toughness for big win over UT

videos.description: The Gators force 18 turnovers and hold the Vols to less than 50 points in a SEC game for the first time in six seasons.
videos.headline: Florida locks the clamps down on No. 6 Tennessee
